10. Deployment
Deployed the Flask API using Render.com

Flask port binding: 0.0.0.0 with PORT env var

Successfully hosted and tested API publicly

 11. API Testing (Live)
Tested using Postman & Thunder Client

POST request to /predict


Input JSON:
{
  "year": 2025,
  "month": 6,
  "day": 10,
  "weekday": 0
}


Response:
{
  "predicted_price": 74.56
}

12. Architecture
User â†’ API Request â†’ Flask App â†’ Load Model â†’ Predict â†’ Return JSON Response
User sends POST request

API processes request

Model makes prediction

Response sent back

 
